                {
                    "path": "resources/img/portrait.jpg",
                    "alt": "portrait of Kristyna"
                },
                "title": "kristýna erbenová",
                "subtitle": "(1987, Czech Republic)",
                "text": "I‘m mainly interested in art photography with a focus on people, landscapes and the relationship between them. In my photography, I‘m trying to bring together the inner world of feelings and thoughts with the outside world of appearances; to create an imaginary space of timelessness; to capture the moments which lead us to a deeper experience of ourselves and the space around us. All my personal projects are shot on medium format film. I'm interested in commissions, collaborations, exhibitions and residences."
